* In many lects, including Standard Mandarin, {{zh-l|兩}} is used when counting things with a measure word, {{zh-l|二}} is used in numbers.
** Examples with {{zh-l|兩}}
**: {{zh-x|兩 個 人|'''two''' people}}
**: {{zh-x|兩 年|'''two''' years}}
**: {{zh-x|兩 百|'''two''' hundred}}
**: {{zh-x|兩 千|'''two''' thousand}}
** Examples with {{zh-l|二}}
**: {{zh-x|二十|twenty|lit='''two''' tens}}
**: {{zh-x|二 百|'''two''' hundred}}
**: {{zh-x|第二|second}}
**: But not {{lang|zh|*'''二'''個人}}
